name: Thicc mommies
author: Kamell
notes: My first KoG and I knew it would come with my new fav archetype Amazoness. The tech options in this deck are super important and are the key to coming out on top of hard or even matchups. Super rush kills geargia and chalice screws Sylvans. TYSM to all the other Amazoness worshipers in the #amazoness channel super helpful guys.
